      "text": "PermitRootLogin: no\nPasswordAuth: no (key-only)\nAuthMethods: publickey\nAllowUsers: <admin-user>\nMaxAuthTries: 3\nLoginGraceTime: 30s\nX11Forwarding: no\nAllowTcpForwarding: no\nCiphers:\n  chacha20-poly1305\n  aes256-gcm\nKEX: curve25519-sha256\nMACs: hmac-sha2-512-etm",
