      "text": "app.service:\n  NoNewPrivileges=true | ProtectSystem=strict | PrivateTmp=true\n  ProtectKernelTunables=true | ProtectControlGroups=true\n  RestrictAddressFamilies=AF_INET,AF_INET6,AF_UNIX,AF_NETLINK\n\nsecret-proxy.service (additional):\n  ProtectHome=true | ProtectKernelModules=true | ProtectKernelLogs=true\n  ReadWritePaths=/run/<app>,/var/log/<app> | ReadOnlyPaths=/etc/<app>",
